<p><a name="Principles_of_insurance" id="Principles_of_insurance"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Insurance&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: Principles of insurance">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Principles of insurance</span></h2>
<table class="toccolours" style="float: right; margin: 0 0 1em 1em; text-align:center; font-size: 90%;">
<tr>
