<li id="cite_note-1"><b><a href="#cite_ref-1" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://www.economicinsurancefacts.org/economics/state/insuredcars/" class="external text" title="http://www.economicinsurancefacts.org/economics/state/insuredcars/" rel="nofollow">"Insured cars by state"</a>. Insurance Information Institute<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.economicinsurancefacts.org/economics/state/insuredcars/" class="external free" title="http://www.economicinsurancefacts.org/economics/state/insuredcars/" rel="nofollow">http://www.economicinsurancefacts.org/economics/state/insuredcars/</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Insured+cars+by+state&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.pub=Insurance+Information+Institute&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.economicinsurancefacts.org%2Feconomics%2Fstate%2Finsuredcars%2F&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Insurance"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
